# Test Fixtures

This directory contains sample data for testing.

## Files

- `sample-transcriptions.json` - Sample transcription data with various scenarios
- `sample-geocoding-responses.json` - Sample geocoding API responses for different providers
- `sample-ai-responses.json` - Sample AI responses for address extraction, categorization, and summaries

## Audio Files

Audio files should be placed in this directory. For testing, you can use:
- Minimal valid MP3 files (headers only)
- Short test audio files (1-5 seconds)
- Various formats (MP3, M4A)

Note: Actual audio files are not included in this repository due to size. They should be generated during test setup or provided separately.
